data.description: Welcome to your ideal home at 9843 foxmoor crk! This charming property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing ample space and comfort. Situated conveniently close to Lackland Air Force Base, it offers easy access to highway 1604, making commuting a breeze. Enjoy the peace of mind with a brand new roof, ensuring years of worry-free living. Don't miss this opportunity to own a cozy residence in a prime location.
